You update your description as follows: Upfront, midrange‑forward lead stacks center‑stage with dense harmonies; bright, hook‑forward synths and orchestral accents; groove‑first production with tight punchy low end, prominent upper‑mid emphasis and synthetic percussion—larger‑than‑life, highly produced sound that sacrifices some transient nuance and intimacy.

